examples.en: Her childhood had been poisoned by an abusive stepfather.

examples.en: She has been trying to detach herself from an abusive relationship.

examples.en: Her face bore all the evidence of the 16-year-long abusive relationship.

examples.en: Women will often lie to shield even the most abusive partner.

examples.en: The shelter offers a haven from abusive spouses.
